io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.InsertionService
public class InsertionServiceElementImpl extends io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.BaseInsertionService<InsertionElement>
Implementation of the BaseInsertionService that processes UI elements annotated with InsertionElement.

This class provides functionality to:

  • Retrieve UI element metadata from InsertionElement annotations.
  • Identify the corresponding ComponentType for a UI element.
  • Build Selenium locators for elements.
  • Perform pre-insertion and post-insertion actions.
  • Sort fields based on their insertion order.

It utilizes an InsertionServiceRegistry to manage different insertion strategies and relies on a SmartWebDriver instance for interacting with web elements.
